\begin_inset Formula $G_{a}$
\end_inset

 at 
\begin_inset Formula $a$
\end_inset

 is just the inverse of that of 
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

, evaluated at 
\begin_inset Formula $g(a)$
\end_inset

:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
G_{a}=\left[F_{g(a)}\right]^{-1}
\]

\end_inset


