\deriv{y(d)}d\define\lim_{d\rightarrow0}\frac{y(d)-y(0)}{d}=\lim_{d\rightarrow0}\frac{1}{d}\log\left[f\left(g\right)^{-1}f\left(ge^{\widehat{de_{i}}}\right)\right]
