 frame in which we choose to represent 
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
v^{n}=\Skew{\omega_{nb}^{n}}p^{n}=\omega_{nb}^{n}\times p^{n}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
